Aim: Consider any Airline Reservation System. Design a database containing tables/fields as route_id, origin, destination, fare, distance, capacity. 
Write a procedure to satisfy the following conditions accepting the route_id as the user  input.
•	If the distance is less than 500 then update the fare to be 190.98
•	If the distance is between 501-1000 then update fare to be 876
•	If the distance is greater than 1000 then display a message.

CREATE TABLE route_header (
    route_id NUMBER(5),
    origin VARCHAR2(20),
    destination VARCHAR2(20),
    fare NUMBER(7,2),
    distance NUMBER(3),
    capacity NUMBER(3)
);


